                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine domini, quod est super omne nomen. <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/261">Chuonradus</persName> divina dispensatione Romanorum
                            <rs key="#Emperor/king">imperator</rs> augustus. Quotienscumque
                        sanctarum ecclesiarum usui prospicimus, imperium nostrum corroboramus, quia
                        communis lingua vocat: sancta ecclesia apud deum intervenire pro
                        benefactoribus non cessat. Quapropter universorum sacrosancte eiusdem
                        ecclesie fidelium nostrorumve presentium nec non et futurorum noverit
                        caritas, quod interventu domini <persName key="#Bishops" ref="#people/288"
                            >Arderici</persName> sancte <placeName key="#Mother_churches"
                            ref="#places/106">Vercellensis</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Mother_churches">ecclesie</rs> venerabilis <rs key="#Bishops"
                            >episcopi</rs> et nostri fidelis karissimi ecclesie sancti Eusebii a deo
                        et a nobis sibi comisse per presentis precepti auctoritatem <rs
                            key="#Imperial/royal_diploma #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >confirmamus</rs> [omnes] donationes concessiones, que supra dicte
                        ecclesie a seculo usque nunc facte sunt a nostris predecessoribus regibus
                        vel imperatoribus, et omnia, que interventu <persName key="#Bishops"
                            ref="#people/171">Leonis</persName>, supra dicti episcopi antecessoris,
                        Constanciae largientes Eusebiane ecclesie nostro precepto addidimus, huic
                        ecclesie pre[fate in perpetuum confirmamus. Et ut omnibus fiat clarius,
                        potissimum concessimus, ut concessa a predecessoribus nostris vel a nobis,
                        nunc autem confirmanda in presentis precepti pagina nominentur expressius,
                        videlicet <rs key="#Comitatus">comitatum</rs>
                        <geogName ref="#estates/131"
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Comitatus #Districtio"
                            >Vercellensem</geogName> cum universis <rs key="#Districtio">publicis
                            functionibus</rs>, totam <rs key="#Cities">civitatem</rs> cum omni
                        publica potestate in integrum et cum omnibus publicis pertinentiis comitatus
                        et civitatis et totum comitatum quem dicunt<geogName ref="#estates/132"
                            key="#Forests #Fisheries #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Castle #Comitatus #Fodrum #Albergaria/gifori #Profits_of_justice #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Districtio #Incastellamento #Public_infrastructures"
                            > sancte Agathe </geogName>imperpetuum cum omnibus <rs key="#Castle"
                            >castellis</rs> villis <rs key="#Fisheries">piscationibus</rs>
                        venationibus <rs key="#Forests">silvis</rs> pratis pascuis <rs
                            key="#Rivers #Lakes #Fluvial_transport #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            >aquis aquarumve decursibus</rs> et omnibus publicis pertinentiis <rs
                            key="#Local_markets">mercatis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Teloneum">theloneis</rs> et cum omnibus publicis functionibus in
                            <placeName
                            key="#Cities #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Local_markets #Profits_of_justice #Teloneum #Districtio"
                            ref="#places/106">civitate Vercellensi</placeName> intus et foris, in
                        toto comitatu Vercellensi et in toto comitatu sancte Agathe intus et foris
                        et in omnibus eorum pertinentiis et ut in castello sancte Agathe et in burgo
                        eius aut per quinque miliaria in circuitu nullus nunquam <rs
                            key="#Profits_of_justice">placitum</rs> teneat aut <rs key="#Fodrum"
                            >fodrum</rs> colligat aut <rs key="#Albergaria/gifori">albergarias</rs>
                        faciat publicas aut publicam exactionem exigat, nisi Vercellensis episcopus
                        aut eius <rs key="#Missus_of_other_public_authorities">missus</rs>, in tota
                        campania nullus theloneum accipiat, nullus mercata habeat publica, nisi
                        Vercellensis ecclesia theloneum et districtum suarum <rs key="#Plebs"
                            >plebium</rs> et super sua habitancium, aquam de Scicida, aquam de
                        Saruo, aquam de Heleuo cum utrisque <rs>ripis</rs> a loco ubi nascuntur
                        usque in Padum, aquam de Pado cum utrisque ripis a
                            <placeName>Lionna</placeName> usque <orgName>plebem Martori,</orgName>
                        aquam de Duria cum utrisque ripis a <placeName>Petra grossa</placeName>
                        usque <placeName ref="#places/183" key="#Rivers">Verucham</placeName>,
                            <placeName>Marascum</placeName>, <geogName ref="#estates/96"
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ><placeName ref="#places/99"
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                >Firminianam</placeName></geogName>, <geogName ref="#estates/63"
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Sestignum</geogName>, <geogName ref="#estates/41"
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ><placeName ref="#places/3"
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                >Carisianam</placeName></geogName> cum utraque ripa, <geogName
                            ref="#estates/62"
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
