                        usque in Padum, Camassaniga et totum Uersade usque in Ampori et totum
                            <placeName ref="#places/529">Andolium</placeName> intra Duriam [et Padum
                        et Zebadasco], sancto Michaeli de Loceio, quicquid <persName ref="#people/9"
                            key="#Emperor/king">Lotharius</persName> augustus donavit, cortem
                            <geogName ref="#estates/195"
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Teloneum #Districtio #Arimannus"
                                ><placeName ref="#places/436"
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Teloneum #Districtio #Arimannus"
                                >Quadradulam</placeName>
                        </geogName>cum districto arimannorum et theloneo, aquam Padi a
                            portu<placeName key="#Ports"> Cleuaxi </placeName>cum utrisque ripis
                        usque ad <placeName>Derum</placeName>, ubi vetus Duria intrat in Padum, et a
                        Dero usque in Mundine et Maminica, <placeName>silvam de Loceio</placeName>
                        et Roncum sicum, <placeName>Conzuningun</placeName> et <placeName>silvam
                            Palazolascam,</placeName>
